statements: SELECT * FROM voice_command_history;
SELECT command_id, user_id, command_text FROM voice_command_history WHERE user_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT * FROM voice_command_history ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT MAX(timestamp) AS latest_timestamp FROM voice_command_history;
SELECT command_text FROM voice_command_history WHERE timestamp >= '2022-01-01' AND timestamp <= '2022-01-31';
SELECT command_id, user_id, command_text, timestamp FROM voice_command_history WHERE user_id = '123' ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT command_id, user_id, command_text, timestamp FROM voice_command_history WHERE timestamp > '2022-01-01' AND timestamp < '2022-01-31';
SELECT user_id, COUNT(command_id) AS command_count FROM voice_command_history GROUP BY user_id HAVING COUNT(command_id) > 5 ORDER BY command_count DESC;
SELECT DISTINCT user_id FROM voice_command_history WHERE command_text LIKE 'Open%';
SELECT command_id, user_id, command_text, timestamp FROM voice_command_history ORDER BY user_id ASC, timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM voice_command_history;
SELECT command_text, timestamp FROM voice_command_history ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT user_id, command_text FROM voice_command_history WHERE user_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT suggestion_text, suggestion_rank, timestamp FROM voice_search_suggestions ORDER BY suggestion_rank ASC;
SELECT * FROM voice_search_suggestions WHERE timestamp >= '2022-01-01 00:00:00';
SELECT * FROM voice_command_history ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT command_text, user_id, timestamp FROM voice_command_history WHERE user_id = 'a1b2c3d4-5678-90e1-f2g3-h4i5j6k7l8m9' ORDER BY timestamp ASC;
SELECT suggestion_text, suggestion_rank FROM voice_search_suggestions WHERE timestamp >= '2022-01-01' AND timestamp <= '2022-12-31' ORDER BY suggestion_rank DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) AS total_commands FROM voice_command_history GROUP BY user_id ORDER BY total_commands DESC;

SELECT command_text, suggestion_text FROM voice_command_history INNER JOIN voice_search_suggestions ON voice_command_history.user_id = voice_search_suggestions.user_id ORDER BY voice_command_history.timestamp ASC, voice_search_suggestions.timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT command_text, timestamp FROM voice_command_history WHERE user_id = 1 ORDER BY timestamp ASC;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) AS command_count FROM voice_command_history GROUP BY user_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 2;

SELECT user_profiles.first_name, user_profiles.last_name, voice_command_history.command_text FROM user_profiles INNER JOIN voice_command_history ON user_profiles.user_id = voice_command_history.user_id;

SELECT u.first_name, u.last_name, COUNT(vc.command_id) AS command_count FROM user_profiles u LEFT JOIN voice_command_history vc ON u.user_id = vc.user_id GROUP BY u.user_id ORDER BY command_count DESC;
